tensura.race.arch_daemon.notes: The peak evolutionary stage that can be reached by daemons in the Daemon Realm. Only the most powerful of greater daemons can ascend to this height.
tensura.race.beast_lord.notes: Beastfolk that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.beastfolk.notes: A race that can freely change between their true animal form and a more a human form. They possess immense physical prowess and regenerative capabilities that let them fight without rest.
tensura.race.daemon_lord.notes: One of the most powerful evolutionary stages of daemons, achieved only by the most powerful arch daemons.
tensura.race.death_oni.notes: Wicked Oni that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.demon_slime.notes: The ultimate stage of evolution of Slimes. They evolve to this stage by awakening as a True Demon Lord during the Harvest Festival.
tensura.race.devil_lord.notes: The final stage of evolution for daemons. One emerges when a daemon meets all three requirements of a name, material body, and divinity.
tensura.race.divine_beast.notes: Beastfolk that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_boar.notes: Orc that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_dragon.notes: Dragonewt that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_dwarf.notes: Dwarf that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_elf.notes: Elf that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_fighter.notes: Wicked Oni that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_fish.notes: Merfolk that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_human.notes: Human that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_oni.notes: Oni that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_skeleton.notes: Wight that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.divine_vampire.notes: Vampire that achieved divinity, possessing an immortal physical body that will never age.
tensura.race.dragonewt.notes: The evolved form of Lizardmen and descendants of dragons. They have an average lifespan of about two hundred years.
tensura.race.dwarf.notes: A sprite race descended from earth elementals. They possess an immense will and make for fierce albeit rather short soldiers.
tensura.race.dwarf_saint.notes: Dwarf that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.elf.notes: A sprite race descended from wind elementals. They possess a fierce talent for elemental magic and are more in tune with nature than most.
tensura.race.elf_saint.notes: Elf that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_dwarf.notes: Dwarf that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_elf.notes: Elf that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_hobgoblin.notes: Hobgoblin that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_human.notes: Human that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_merfolk.notes: Merfolk that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.enlightened_ogre.notes: Ogre that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Demi-Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.ghoul.notes: A vampiric thrall brought about by Blood Raise, highly weakened by sunlight.
tensura.race.goblin.notes: A race of Sprite Demi-Humans. They seem to be descended from the offspring of Dwarves and Oni.
tensura.race.god_slime.notes: The divine stage of evolution of Slimes.
tensura.race.greater_daemon.notes: The daemon race that lesser daemons evolve to when they develop their ego and accumulate enough power.
tensura.race.high_orc.notes: The evolved form of Orcs. They are smarter than Orcs while preserving the Orc race's special characteristics, with appearance virtually identical to regular Orcs.
tensura.race.hobgoblin.notes: The evolved form of male Goblins that is ranked D on average.
tensura.race.hobgoblin_saint.notes: Hobgoblin that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.human.notes: A weak but populous race that relies more on technology and numbers than brute force. Their low magicule count makes skills and magic users a rarity among them, instead favouring battlewill.
tensura.race.human_saint.notes: Human that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.kijin.notes: A race of Sprite Demi-Humans descended from Fire Elementals. They have an average lifespan of over a thousand years
tensura.race.lesser_daemon.notes: The lowest level of the daemon race. They spontaneously come into existence within the Daemon Realm where they slowly accumulate experience from fighting and being summoned before eventually evolving into greater daemons.
tensura.race.lizardman.notes: A race of scaled people descended from dragons. Their webbed feet give them an advantage in wet terrain.
tensura.race.merfolk.notes: A sprite race descended from water elementals. Their fish-like bodies give them an insurmountable advantage in water.
tensura.race.merfolk_saint.notes: Merfolk that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.metal_slime.notes: A slime that has taken in large quantities of Magic Ore. The dissolved ore inside of it provides a strong resistance towards most forms of damage.
tensura.race.mystic_oni.notes: The result of Kijin fully returning to their roots as Elementals, making them Spiritual Lifeforms.
tensura.race.ogre.notes: A sprite race descended from fire elementals. They possess immense physical capabilities and a strong Japanese lineage.
tensura.race.orc.notes: A race of beastfolk who lost the ability to shift between man and beast, resulting in a permanent mix of the two. Their physical strength is greater than average but pails in comparison to their original strength as beastfolk.
tensura.race.orc_disaster.notes: The evolution of an Orc Lord that is a Demon Lord Seed.
tensura.race.orc_lord.notes: A very rare and powerful member of the Orc race with high intelligence who appears roughly every few centuries.
tensura.race.selection.random_race: A race randomly selected from a configurable list of options, adding an element of unpredictability to the experience. Are you willing to take the risk?
tensura.race.slime.notes: A Spectral race of monster that lacks intelligence and ambition. They’re usually passive but are incredibly ruthless once provoked.
tensura.race.spirit_beast.notes: Beastfolk that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.spirit_boar.notes: Orc that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.spirit_oni.notes: Oni that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.spirit_skeleton.notes: Wight that has "evolved the correct way" and became a Spiritual Lifeform.
tensura.race.true_dragonewt.notes: The evolution of Dragonewts and complete Spiritual Lifeforms. They are the second-highest evolutionary stage of Dragonewt known to exist.
tensura.race.vampire.notes: A race of Majin with nearly eternal life. Although they can reproduce, they normally abstain. Hosting overwhelming magical energy and vitality, their flesh never decays.
tensura.race.vampire_lord.notes: A vampire among the loftiest levels of power, comparable to a Demon Lord.
tensura.race.vampire_overcomer.notes: Vampires that have evolved to overcome their weakness against the sun.
tensura.race.wicked_oni.notes: A variant of Oni, possessing an essence that leans closer towards that of a Daemon rather than that of a pure Elemental.
tensura.race.wight.notes: A Demi-Spiritual skeletal Undead Monster, highly weakened by sunlight.
tensura.race.wight_king.notes: A type of Undead Monster and an evolution of Wights. They possess fearsome power comparable to that of Demon Lord Seeds.

tensura.skill.all_seeing_eye.description: Go into a 3rd person mode, with your increased POV you gain movement and action buffs as well as an upgrade to Presence Sense.
tensura.skill.analytical_appraisal.descr: Assess the strength of your opponents to gain insight into their overall strength.

tensura.skill.beast_transformation.descr: Transform into a beast to restore your vitality and boost your physical body. The transformation will grant great physical prowess but leave a toll on your body.
tensura.skill.berserk.description: Massively empower your body and infuse it with a flame aura. Allows you to go into a risky but overwhelmingly powerful berserker mode.
tensura.skill.berserker.description: Feed on your enemies' defeat. Gain EP from kills, destroy equipment faster, and boost your physical stats based on your power level.
tensura.skill.bewilder.description: Manipulate friends and foes, compelling them to act according to your will.
tensura.skill.black_flame.description: Command the tempest infused flames to spew out black flames at your enemies or even shoot deadly fireballs and hell flares.
tensura.skill.black_lightning.descriptio: Shoot black lightning at varying strength, or summon a massive storm which attacks any non-allied mobs. A short range plasma blast can also be used to melt even the strongest of foes.
tensura.skill.blizzard.description: Creates a powerful storm of ice to slow your enemies and turn the tides of battle.
tensura.skill.blood_mist.description: Spill your own blood to summon a mist which steals the vitality of your enemies and can be blown up to harm any nearby entities or shoot a powerful blood beam.
tensura.skill.body_armor.description: Protect yourself from harm by summoning armoursaurus scales around your body.
tensura.skill.body_double.description: Use a tenth of your magical power to summon an identical clone which takes increased damage but will fight for you until the end. The user can exchange places with the clone but risk taking increased damage.
tensura.skill.chant_annulment.descriptio: Become able to cast mastered magic instantly, in water or even under the effects of silence.
tensura.skill.charm.description: Use your inherent power to turn your opponents neutral or to temporarily dominate weak opponents.
tensura.skill.chef.description: Purify and renew. Remove all negative effects and restore vitality to those under your care.
tensura.skill.chosen_one.description: Radiate authority and charisma to force fear into the hearts of your enemies and to make them follow you instead, while empowering yourself and your allies.
tensura.skill.coercion.description: Shoot a blast of roar in front of you scaring any afflicted entities.
tensura.skill.cold_resistance.descriptio: Ignore weak cold damage or resist the damage of powerful attacks.
tensura.skill.commander.description: Lead the charge with your allies. Empower yourself and your allies to give yourself an overwhelming advantage.
tensura.skill.cook.description: Bend reality to ensure your enemies meet their demise by ignoring their dodge and barriers.
tensura.skill.corrosion.description: Empower your attacks with the deadly effect of Corrosion, toggleable when mastered.
tensura.skill.corrosion_resistance.descr: Ignore weak corrosive effects or reduce the damage from stronger corrosive attacks.
tensura.skill.creator: Creator
tensura.skill.creator.description: Create any Unique Skill and use it for a limited amount of time.
tensura.skill.danger_sense.description: Receive a mental warning when entities with hostile intent enter your proximity.
tensura.skill.dark_cube.description: Create a cube of darkness that slows movement and deals constant damage.
tensura.skill.dark_eight_palms.descripti: Experimental Feature! - Launch up to eight devastating aura blasts at foes.
tensura.skill.darkness.description: Call on your spirit to reduce the enemy's vision in a wide area.
tensura.skill.darkness_attack_resistance: Ignore weaker darkness damage or reduce the damage of stronger attacks.
tensura.skill.darkness_cannon.descriptio: Shoot a long beam which deals massive damage, destroys armor and debilitates enemies.
tensura.skill.darkness_transform.descrip: Channel your inner darkness to burn and blind nearby opponents.
tensura.skill.death_march_dance.descript: Experimental Feature! - Gather your aura into a ring of devastating aura spheres that come crashing down.
tensura.skill.degenerate.description: Craft, decraft, customize items and absorb strength from weakened enemies.
tensura.skill.demon_lord_haki.descriptio: Unleash your Demonic aura causing those around you to quake in fear.
tensura.skill.diamond_path.description: Experimental Feature! - Harden your aura around you to block incoming attacks.
tensura.skill.divine_berserker.descripti: Empower your body by a massive amount but beware the aftereffects.
tensura.skill.divine_ki_release.descript: Use your Divine Ki to amplify your battlewill to deal more damage and destroy weaker equipment.
tensura.skill.dragon_ear.description: Use your sensitive hearing to precisely pin the location of any nearby mobs which make sound.
tensura.skill.dragon_eye.description: Use your powerful sight to access the power of any entities and see in the far distance.
tensura.skill.dragon_mode.description: Once a day, draw out your monstrous potential to double your EP and to boost your physical prowess. Doing this will leave a temporary toll on your body.
tensura.skill.dragon_skin.description: Transform your skin into scales which become tougher as you gain more EP.
tensura.skill.drain.description: Steal the vitality of your opponent and temporarily transform this skill into one of theirs to potentially turn the tables.
tensura.skill.earth.description: Place down blocks which mimic those from the surrounding environment.
tensura.skill.earth_attack_resistance.de: Ignore weak earth-based damage or resist the damage from powerful attacks.
tensura.skill.earth_domination.descripti: Boosts the power of  Earth abilities by a large amount.
tensura.skill.earth_jail.description: Restrict and weaken a single target, applying debuffs to allow you to finish them off.
tensura.skill.earth_manipulation.descrip: Boosts the power of Earth abilities by a decent amount.
tensura.skill.earth_spikes.description: Raises a spike under your opponent launching them into the air.
tensura.skill.earth_storm.description: Summons a viscous sandstorm and falling rocks around you.
tensura.skill.earth_transform.descriptio: Channel the powers of the earth to deal increased damage and increase local gravity around you.
tensura.skill.earthshatter_kick.descript: Experimental Feature! - Stomp your foot down upheaving the land around you.
tensura.skill.electricity_resistance.des: Ignore weak electrical damage or resist the damage from stronger attacks.
tensura.skill.electro_blast.description: Fire a beam attack that pierces through enemies and deals devastating damage while paralyzing your enemies.
tensura.skill.elephant_stampede.descript: Experimental Feature! - Throw a ring of aura spheres around you.
tensura.skill.engorger.description: Increase your size and boost your physical stats.
tensura.skill.envy.description: Absorb strength from enemies, buff yourself and debilitate your enemies.
tensura.skill.eye_of_truth.description: By obtaining the mythical Hero Egg, the veil of deception is torn apart. No illusion or concealment can deceive your sight, and your vision becomes perfect.
tensura.skill.falsifier.description: See through falsehoods and invisibility, conceal your presence from prying eyes and create illusions.
tensura.skill.farsight.description: Focus your eyes and become able to see things far away.
tensura.skill.fighter.description: Achieve mastery through discipline. Learn combat and magic abilities instantly, gain more mastery points, and hit much harder.
tensura.skill.fire.description: Use your spirit to start a small fire.
tensura.skill.fire_breath.description: Breathe flames and incinerate your enemies.
tensura.skill.flame_attack_resistance.de: Ignore weaker flame damage or resist the damage from more powerful flames.
tensura.skill.flame_breath.description: Spew fire to burn away enemies and set fire to the land.
tensura.skill.flame_domination.descripti: Boosts the power of fire abilities by a large amount.
tensura.skill.flame_manipulation.descrip: Boosts the power of fire abilities by a decent amount.
tensura.skill.flame_transform.descriptio: Channel the powers of fire to burn all nearby foes.
tensura.skill.flare_circle.description: Opens a Gate to Hell from which wicked flames erupt to turn your enemies to ash.
tensura.skill.formhide.description: Experimental Feature! - Match your aura to the surroundings, which makes you imperceptible.
tensura.skill.fusionist.description: Turn the world into a weapon, absorb the environment to create powerful mines and grenades.
tensura.skill.gate.description: Tear space asunder connecting two points in space.
tensura.skill.gluttony.description: Absorb all in your path. None can win. Receive and provide skills, gain access to a spatial storage and mimic entities.
tensura.skill.godly_craftsman.descriptio: Utilize your years of experience to create masterpieces with ease and engrave your weapons for terrifying efficiency.
tensura.skill.godwolf_sense.description: Improve your senses to be able to see in the dark or even spot invisible entities nearby.
tensura.skill.gourmand.description: Feast on the energy of your opponents. Steal magicule with your attacks and become more powerful when killing others.
tensura.skill.gourmet.description: Absorb your enemies, gain new powers, and break down anything that stands in your way.

tensura.skill.gravity_domination.descrip: Boosts Gravity abilities by a large amount and allows you to fly without hindrance.
tensura.skill.gravity_field.description: Weaken gravity around yourself to make movement easier or create a variously sized sphere granting previous effects while debuffing enemies.
tensura.skill.gravity_flight.description: Manipulate gravity to allow flight, your momentum from before will be continued.
tensura.skill.gravity_manipulation.descr: Boosts Gravity abilities by a decent amount and allows you to fly without hindrance.
tensura.skill.great_sage.description: Improve your cognitive skills to learn and cast faster, become able to appraise targets and use analysis to copy skills and process materials to craft or clone items or equipment.
tensura.skill.greed.description: Take everything. Conquer the world and your enemies with it. Kill anyone who stands in your path while strengthening yourself or your allies.
tensura.skill.guardian.description: Stand as a bastion against the force of your enemies. Absorb the damage from your allies and fortify their defenses.
tensura.skill.haki.description: Project your aura to cow nearby foes into submission.
tensura.skill.haze.description: Experimental Feature! - Wrap yourself in a cloak of aura concealing yourself from even the most heightened of senses.
tensura.skill.healer.description: Mend wounds with a touch or unleash devastating afflictions, capable of both salvation and suffering.
tensura.skill.heat_resistance.descriptio: Ignore weaker heat-based damage or reduce the damage from stronger heat sources.
tensura.skill.heat_wave.description: Shoot a fiery projectile or summon a short-ranged fire storm which will damage all nearby entities.
tensura.skill.heavenly_eye.description: Project your otherworldly gaze to see all nearby entities and partially ignore dodging abilities.
tensura.skill.heavy_slash.description: Experimental Feature! - Channel your aura into your arms and bring down a mountain-splitting slash.
tensura.skill.hellfire.description: Summon a sphere of hellfire to deal massive damage in a small area.
tensura.skill.hero_haki.description: Use your Hero Aura to inspire your allies and terrify your enemies.
tensura.skill.holy_attack_resistance.des: Ignore weaker holy attacks or reduce the damage from stronger divine powers.
tensura.skill.hydraulic_propulsion.descr: Propel yourself at high speeds underwater.
tensura.skill.infinite_regeneration.desc: Use your massive amount of magicule to instantly regenerate from all but the most grievous of injuries.
tensura.skill.infinity_prison.descriptio: Trap enemies in an unbreakable dimensional cage or shield yourself from any threat with your dimensional barrier. Gain access to spatial storage.
tensura.skill.instant_move.description: Experimental Feature! - Gather your aura at your feet to travel faster than the eye can see.
